Articles.Content:
The Long March 5 has completed it's final core test and the final phase before pre-flight testing. The rocket can now be shipped to Wenchang for similar tests to what the LM-7 was doing 2 months ago.

As well as this they have been nice enough to create a montage of the LM-5's construction and testing: [http://www.miaopai.com/show/0pZy8Co2fxpO8jJCAkpRqw__.htm](http://www.miaopai.com/show/0pZy8Co2fxpO8jJCAkpRqw__.htm)
Way to go, China ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif) Let's hope this new rocket will serve well.
